Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The 10th CPC Congress of Weihai City was held in 
Weihai from 20 to 23 December. At the first session of the 10th 
city party committee, a new leading body was elected. Comrade 
Zang Haiqiang was elected secretary of the city party committee; 
and Wu Longjiang, Sun Shoupu, Cui Yuechen (1508 2574 5256), and 
Lian Chengmin (6647 2110 2404) were elected deputy secretaries 
of the committee. At the first meeting of the discipline 
inspection commission under the Weihai city party committee, 
held at the same time, Comrade Xue Hongzhen (5641 3163 2182) was 
