Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Asmara, January 13 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Foreign 
Minister Qian Qichen wound up his two-day visit to Eritrea today 
and left for the Sudan. 
  During his visit to Eritrea, Qian Qichen, who is also 
Chinese 
