<H3> <TI>   Chengdu Military Region Studies Deng's Theory </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK1301131094 Chengdu Sichuan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK1301131094 </F>
<F P=104>  Chengdu Sichuan People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Yesterday some cadres at the regimental-level 
and above, as well as advanced individuals from different units 
of the Chengdu Military Region, gathered in Chengdu to 
participate in a meeting on studying Comrade Deng Xiaoping's 
theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics, his 
thought on Army building in the new period, and General 
Secretary Jiang Zemin's instructions on Army building. Among 
present in the front row at the meeting were: Chengdu Military 
Regional leaders Li Jiulong, Zhang Zhijian, Liao Xilong, and Zhu 
Chengyou; provincial party Secretary Xie Shijie; and Govenor 
Xiao Yang. 
  Commander Li Jiulong addressed the meeting amid warm 
applause. After reviewing work in the last five years, he said: 
The objective for the military region's reform and construction 
in the coming five years is to profoundly implement the spirit 
of the 14th CPC National Congress and the strategic policy for 
the new period, to arm the three services with Comrade Deng 
Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese 
characteristics and his thought on Army building, to ensure 
stability in the armed forces and border areas, to maintain 
social stability, and to provide a powerful safety guarantee for 
the country's reform, opening up, and modernization. [passage 
omitted] 

