<F P=100> Military </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shenyang Military Region Commander Visits Jilin </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1601042394 Changchun Jilin People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1030 GMT 15 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1601042394 </F>
<F P=104>  Changchun Jilin People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Wang Ke, commander of the Shenyang Military Region; 
and Li Xinliang, political commissar of the Shenyang Military 
Region, who came to our province to inspect the army units and 
the militia work, went to the provincial military district a few 
days ago to meet with the commanders and fighters of the organs 
under the provincial military district. 
  After hearing the work reports made by Zhou Zaikang, 
commander of the provincial military district, and Shi Zhaonian, 
political commissar of the provincial military district, 
Commander Wang Ke and Political Commissar Li Xinliang gave 
important instructions to the party organizations at various 
levels in the provincial military district in regard to how to 
implement the theory on building socialism with Chinese 
characteristics and Comrade Deng Xiaoping's ideology governing 
the army building in the new situation, to comprehensively 
strengthen the building of militia and reserve duty forces, and 
to enhance the border defense work. Simultaneously, they fully 
affirmed and praised the provincial military district's 
achievements in mobilizing the militia and reserve duty forces 
to help the local governments fulfill the extremely difficult, 
dangerous, and heavy tasks, and positively engage themselves in 
economic construction. 
  Commander Wang Ke and Political Commissar Li Xinliang also 
urged commanders and soldiers of the provincial military 
district and all militiamen across the province to ceaselessly 
keep forging ahead in the course of reform and to make new 
contributions to realizing the target of building a developed, 
border, near-the-sea province, and building the national defense 
reserve forces. 

</TEXT>

