  [Text] Shanghai, January 17 (XINHUA) -- Visiting former 
U.S. President George Bush said here today that Sino-U.S. 
relations are the most important relations in the world and he 
had never changed his views on this point. 
  He added that it would be beneficial to both sides for 
Sino-U.S. friendly relations to get as fast as possible onto a 
