  [Text] Beijing, January 19 (XINHUA) -- U.S. Secretary of 
Treasury Lloyd Bentsen arrived here this afternoon for a 
four-day official goodwill visit to China. 
  The visit will serve to resume work of the Sino-U.S. Joint 
Economic Commission, which last met in 1987. 
  During his stay in Beijing, Bentsen is expected to meet 
